about: I build software for the web and mobile applications for both IOS and android. My journey started back in 2013 when I saw all the cool projects my friend was buiding. I started going to an internet cafe to watch youtube courses on php.
It was fun most of the time I had no idea what I was doing. Fast foward I have acquired mathematical, technical, logical skills.
I love working and sharing with people on things I have built and learnt.
